      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Consumed View Switching Smoke Test\n\nThis graph tests the final consumed-view model:\n\n- one fixed consumer node type: `port`\n- one explicit source node address: `/tasks/ui-analysis/consumed-view-switching-smoke.node#smoke-source-summary`\n- one explicit selected view: `sourcePayload`\n\n## Checks\n\n1. Select `Switch Me`.\n2. In **Behavior**, confirm the Node Address resolves to the source node.\n3. Change **Consumed View** between `node.web.summary`, `node.web.detail`, and `node.web.icon`.\n4. Confirm the same `port` node changes surface without changing its runtime type.\n5. Use the prewired `Detail` and `Icon` consumers as comparison targets."
      }
    },
