      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Contract Under Test\n\nThe `port` renderer should remain the host surface.\n\n- `sourceRef` + `sourceNodeId` identify the source node.\n- `sourcePayload` selects the consumed view.\n- `consumerKind` may classify intent, but it must **not** become runtime node type.\n\nIf switching works, then this graph proves the UI can author the final consumed-view model directly."
      }
